# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values.
# `.env` is gitignored — it never gets pushed to GitHub.
#
# Claude Code expands ${VAR} references in .mcp.json from your
# shell environment. Load this file before launching Claude:
#   PowerShell:  Get-Content .env | ForEach-Object { if ($_ -match '^\s*([^#=]+)=(.*)$') { [Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable($matches[1].Trim(), $matches[2].Trim()) } }
#   bash/zsh:    set -a && source .env && set +a
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ===== ACTIVE: Gmail ============================================
# Path to the Google Cloud OAuth client keys downloaded from GCP.
# One client can authorize many Gmail accounts; per-account tokens
# are written next to it by the `auth` step (see README).
GMAIL_OAUTH_PATH=./config/credentials/gcp-oauth.keys.json


# ===== OPTIONAL providers (uncomment when you add them) =========
# To enable: add the matching server block from ./providers/ into
# .mcp.json, then uncomment + fill the vars below. See providers/README.md.

# --- IMAP / SMTP account (template: providers/imap.provider.json) ---
# IMAP_FASTMAIL_HOST=imap.fastmail.com
# IMAP_FASTMAIL_PORT=993
# SMTP_FASTMAIL_HOST=smtp.fastmail.com
# SMTP_FASTMAIL_PORT=465
# IMAP_FASTMAIL_USER=you@fastmail.com
# IMAP_FASTMAIL_PASSWORD=app-specific-password-here   # NOT your main password

# --- Outlook / Microsoft 365 (template: providers/outlook.provider.json) ---
# OUTLOOK_WORK_TENANT_ID=...
# OUTLOOK_WORK_CLIENT_ID=...
# OUTLOOK_WORK_CLIENT_SECRET=...
# OUTLOOK_WORK_USER=you@company.com
